'''Bujumbura''' ni umurwa mukuru w'igihugu c'[[Uburundi]] mu vyerekeye Ubutunzi.
* ''[[Uburinganire]]'': Ibirometero kwadarato 127
* ''[[Abanyagihugu]]'': 1096647 (2019)
* ''[[Ukurundana]]'': Abantu 8605 ku kirometero kwadarato

Bujumbura n'umurwa mukuru w'uburundi muvyerekeye Ubutunzi inyuma y'aho Gitega ibaye umurwa mukuru wa politike. Nico gisagara cambere kinini mu Burundi kigatera caguka. Muri 2008 cari gifise uburinganire bungana n'ibirometero kwadarato 87 Ubu naho kikaba kigeze ku birometero kwadarato 127.Ico gisagara cahora gifise Ama komine 13 Ubu naho kikaba gifise Ama komine 3 inyuma y'ingaburo nshasha y'ico gisagara.Ayo makomine atatu akaba ari Muha,Mukaza na Ntahangwa.Komine Ntahangwa ikaba iherereye mu buraruko bw'ico gisagara ikagarukira ku ruzi Ntahangwa,komine Mukaza nayo ikaba iherereye hagati, ikaba iri hagati y'uruzi Ntahangwa na Muha.Komine Muha Iherereye Mu bumanuko bw'ico gisagara igahera ku ruzi Muha itera imanuka.

